<h2 class="cover-top">Third Annual</h2>
<h1 class="cover-heading">Indian Summer Guac-Off</h1>
<dl class="dl-horizontal">
  <dt class="invitation-side">About</dt>
  <dd class="invitation-body">
    The Annual Indian Summer Guac-off is a party that showcases the best guacamole's that the City has to offer.
    The fine humans of San Francisco will get to decide who has the best guacamole in the City.
    The winner to be crowned with the guacamole glory trophy, bragging rights until next Indian summer, the title of official "Guacamole of San Francisco", and a secret mystery prize!
  </dd>

  <dt class="invitation-side">Rules</dt>
  <dd class="invitation-body">
    Entry into the competition is free.
    Your guacamole must use at least 6 avocados.
    For all others wishing to attend, you must fairly judge the guacamole's presented.
  </dd>

  <dt class="invitation-side">Prizes</dt>
  <dd class="invitation-body">
    Stellar prizes from some stellar local companies!
  </dd>

  <dt class="invitation-side">Location</dt>
  <dd class="invitation-body">
    Saturday, Sept 13th, 2013<br>
    SOMEWHERE AWESOME TBD<br>
    2pm - until the last chip is eaten
  </dd>
</dl>

<form class="form-horizontal lead" role="form" action="/" method="post">
  <div class="form-group">
    <div class="col-sm-6 col-centered">
      <input class="form-control" type="text" name="name" placeholder="Guacamole Champ" required>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="form-group">
    <div class="col-sm-6 col-centered">
      <input class="form-control" type="text" name="email" placeholder="guac-lover@gmail.com" required>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="form-group">
    <div class="checkbox-header">What are you bringing?</div>

    <label class="checkbox-inline" for="guac">
      <input type="checkbox" value="option1" name="guac">Guac
    </label>
    <label class="checkbox-inline" for="beer">
      <input type="checkbox" value="option2" name="beer">Beer
    </label>
    <label class="checkbox-inline" for="other">
      <input type="checkbox" value="option3" name="other">Other
    </label>
  </div>
  <button type="submit" class="btn btn-lg btn-success">Count me in!</button>
</form>
